<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="728" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="20.[194,1404,278,786]" pageId="20" pageNumber="728">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[196,307,278,311]" pageId="20" pageNumber="728">Habitat.</emphasis>
Primary and secondary lowland and montane forest, including lower edges of mossy forest. The Mindanao Squirrelis also found in agricultural areas.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
