<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="728" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="20.[194,1404,278,786]" pageId="20" pageNumber="728">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[195,543,593,626]" pageId="20" pageNumber="728">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Mindanao Squirrelis widely distributed, occurs in a number of protected areas, and is tolerant to some degree of habitat modification. Potential threats are the illegal pet trade and hunting for local consumption.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
